body:
Hey @StephenOman thanks!

The new file contains the proper model

I still can't build the lib with the `DecodeJPEG` op for some reason, did you change something to the build file when you built it? The jpeg files seem to be explicitly removed from the `contrib` build in `gen_file_lists.sh` https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/3c5233d54d3dc431bdee2a5756cc2f1f9b270503/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/gen_file_lists.sh#L22

Thanks for Eigen -- so I should update the hash in the Makefile, can you tell which one you are using?
